Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.57,0:01:23.35,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&HBC9800&\c&HFFF4C5&}yudan shitara sono yubi chiku chiku atakku kakugo shite
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.57,0:01:23.35,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HBC9800&\c&HFFFFFF&}Kada ne budeš pazio, očekuj moje prste da krenu u napad golicanjem.
